title: Gitcoin Steward Council Election
description:
Summary:
This proposal is to elect the 10 members to the Gitcoin Steward Council.  The new Steward Council will have a term of 180 days (term: ~ 05 December 2022 to ~03 June 2023).

Following Proposal: V2 of the Steward Council 1, the Gitcoin Workstreams identified 3 nominees per work stream and those nominees were reviewed by CSDO.   Those nominees are listed here for your consideration.  

Candidate biographies and details on how this vote will be conducted can be read on the forum listed below.

title: SMA 2-for-1 'split' + Governance Rewards
description:
*Requirements:* 
- Being a holder of an NFT of the StupidMonkeys Animated Collection or 10 different NFTs of the StupidMonkeys Pajamas Collection

*Vote proposal:*
- It has been a long journey so far even if we have just started, and we are now focused on the next big chapter of our roadmap, our second main collection, and the game.
We have heard your suggestions and while we think that our first main collection, StupidMonkeys Animated, will continue to have a decisive role even after the release of the second collection and the game, we are asking you to vote on this important aspect: the price of the collection NFTs.
A lot of things have impacted the crypto/NFTs markets during the last couple of months, so this proposal is about reducing the price of an SMA NFT from 0.222eth to 0.111eth.
Of course, we won't leave behind our beloved holders and supporters, and for this reason, if this proposal will pass, we will then randomly airdrop another SMA NFT for free to each holder, based on the number of SMA held ( one new SMA NFT per SMA NFT previously held ).
If so, the total SMA NFTs available ( as of today 11.29.2022 ) will be reduced to 315, at a more affordable price, with the goal of increasing the community.

This voting proposal also gives the voters the possibility to claim their governance rewards, so if you want them please make sure to vote.

Thank you for your vote.

*NFT Marketplace Listing*
- https://nft.gamestop.com/user/StupidMonkeysNFT?tab=created

*Relevant Links*
- https://stupidmonkeys.co/
- https://twitter.com/StupidMonkey741
- https://discord.gg/87ZvAXj5w6

*NFT Collections Description*
- The Premium Collection of 741 unique NFTs is our state-of-the-art foundation that provides long-term value for its holders. Each holder is eligible to vote on the critical decisions of our project and, being the first buyer of the monkey (so from our wallet address), entitles the holder to receive the respective digital twin of the StupidMonkeys Verse Collection. The NFTs have 138 unique rarity traits and they differ for at least 4 traits. 
We donate 30% of the total sales to the wildlife charity Gorillafund to help our beloved monkeys.

title: As of December 31, 2022, where do you think the price of SQUID will be?
Reserve 5% of $DOGENS for Founding Dogens (all 500 LP providing NFTs)
description:
![Vote-header.png](ipfs://bafkreia5bvk23vaxfgtohxnnydavmlzd3t3pg7z2yyfwgrxo4kxqqslaxu)
    
Fellow Dogens,

As our devs are preparing the token contracts we had some discussion on how to keep this a fair launch, but also enable you, our loyal co-founders, to get in on the ground floor. 

As you may know, most launches get raided by bots, snipers and jeets in the first minute. This probably means the loyals in here only can buy tokens at higher prices than those rippers. We have therefor suggested to reserve a small number of tokens for the 500 NFT holders who have enabled us to raise a very solid amount of starting liquidity. 

Our suggestion would be to give every NFT an airdrop of 66.99 $DOGENS, which amounts up to 33,495 tokens in reserve. That‚Äôs roughly 5% of total supply. The other 95% of tokens will still go into liquidity. To keep this launch as fair as possible, we want to lock those tokens for 15 days, so there will be no sell pressure from founders at launch. 

We already had a fair poll on this subject in this channel during the time of NFT sales. The poll was closed once the NFTs were sold out. This way we ensured everyone that participated in the poll had a fair chance to buy NFTs while voting.

The result of the vote was 58% yes and 42% no. This means we now must put this up for a final vote in the DAO that yesterday was successfully upgraded to all 500 NFTs.

VOTE!

title: LIP-5 Migrate to a new contract to support OpenSea's blocklist
description:
# Summary

OpenSea has [released a blog post](https://opensea.io/blog/announcements/on-creator-fees/) about a new blocklist feature intended to
enforce creator fees on secondary sales.

This is a proposal to migrate to a new contract that attempts to enforces creator fees on chain using [the OpenSea OperatorFilterRegistry tool](https://github.com/ProjectOpenSea/operator-filter-registry). This will allow us to support OpenSea's blocklist and remain eligible for creator fees from secondary sales on OpenSea.

# Motivation

OpenSea has stated that they will not support creator fees for new collections that don't use the OperatorFilterRegistry tool. Loot currently has a 5% creator fee, which may be lost if we don't migrate to a new contract.

# Specifications

The new contract will be deployed to Ethereum mainnet. Existing Loot holders will be able to migrate their Loot to the new contract by calling a function on the new contract. The migrate function will burn the legacy Loot and mint new Loot on the new contract with the same ID. Migrating will be free and just cost gas.

title: [BGYC1] Implementation of decentralized voting system
description:
A few months ago, we made the choice to make BGYC a community project. We got a % of the royalties to feed the community wallet, built a team, deployed a multisig, built the foundations:

Now It's time to take a further step towards decentralization with the **implementation of votes by Snapshot!**

The goal is to allow the community to master the decision-making process and to fully express its potential. To ensure that your words are heard and that you are aligned with the direction of the project, to build always more, always better together!

![600x200.jfif](ipfs://bafkreias6sa3dzguqegkhfijzbrq6js5aymxd4t3e2ytzfwrimxzjq27e4)


**Our votes are settled in the following ways:**
*ALL BGYC holders can vote
*ALL BGYC holders can make a new proposal
*1 gorilla = 1 vote
*Quorum = 7,5% / 750 gorillas
*Voting duration: 7 days


*The team reserves the right to delete a proposal if it endangers the project (governance attack, legal issues), is spam or is totally impossible to implement*
*Quorum rules and voting times may be adjusted later to better accommodate attendance*

"Plants vs. Zombies 3" is the third puzzle strategy tower defense game after "Plants vs. Zombies 2: A Wonderful Time Journey" and "Plants vs. Zombies: Heroes".Gained popularity among players.

PopCap officially enters the blockchain game field, It is currently planned to release Plants vs. Zombies 3 for the first time in Shark DAO, while maintaining the design features, adding blockchain, NFT, Web3, metaverse technologies and elements, and will develop Plants vs. Zombies 3 NFT, NFT props, etc. to enhance the NFT game. Playability and value-added.

special treatment
Shark DAO members airdrop game tokens and NFT props
Users participating in proposals and voting will be whitelisted
Users will be whitelisted when PopCap releases more blockchain games in the future

Feel free to let us know if you have any suggestions to enrich Plants vs. Zombies 3.

Required quorum: 10,000 (if no quorum is exceeded, the proposal will require more than 90% of the votes cast to pass)
Voting time: 90 days

EFP-5: EarthFund DAO to contribute assets to newly formed entity
description:
## Summary:

* EarthFund DAO will seek to raise money from institutional investors.
* EarthFund DAO will form a new Delaware entity (‚ÄúNewco‚Äù) through which the investment funds will be raised.
* The investment monies will be used to continue the development of the Newco platform and further market EarthFund‚Äôs solutions.
* EarthFund DAO will contribute assets (i.e., all intellectual property, including but not limited to brand, platform, and software) to Newco in exchange for 20% of the equity of Newco. 

## Motivation: 

In the last quarter, we‚Äôve been meeting with investors intending to secure between $12M and $15M in venture capital to continue the development and growth of the EarthFund platform.

**Conversations are heading in a positive direction, but to secure investment, they wanted to see three things:**

* A team of experienced entrepreneurs, advisors, and team members that have what it takes to build a winning product. (We satisfy all criteria.)
* A working product with a strong addressable market and functionality. (We satisfy all criteria.)
* A roadmap for growth with no barriers to execution. (We have a roadmap and a clear strategy for growth, but we need to secure investment to really scale up our efforts and grow the team with the view of growing EarthFund into a billion-dollar company.)

And due to the legal uncertainty of DAOs, the role of the EarthFund DAO was another barrier for investors. 

As such, our advisors have recommended establishing a new company‚Ää‚Äî‚ÄäEarthFund Inc‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääto own and control the assets and intellectual property of EarthFund. 

Because we didn‚Äôt want to remove or reduce the role of the EarthFund DAO in the management of the platform, vetting causes and helping shape the projects/causes on the platform, we came up with the following solution.


### **Our proposal for the relationship between EarthFund and the new company**

The management of EarthFund DAO proposes the following:

* **EarthFund DAO will seek to raise money** from institutional investors.
* **EarthFund DAO will form a new Delaware entity** (‚ÄúNewco‚Äù) through which the investment funds will be raised.
* The **investment monies will be used to continue the development of the Newco platform** and further market EarthFund‚Äôs solutions.
* EarthFund DAO has recently created and launched a DAO launchpad, KYC solution, donation router, grant/rewards contract, token minting tool, Discord bot, and more‚Ä¶ all of which enable prospective customers to launch a decentralized community without spending months or years developing their own platform.
* **EarthFund DAO will contribute assets **(i.e., all intellectual property, including but not limited to brand, platform, and software)** to Newco in exchange for 20% of the equity of Newco.** (The remaining equity in Newco will be allocated to investors and to current and future Newco leadership as an incentive.)
* **EarthFund DAO will receive common shares of Newco** with no voting rights except as described below.
* EarthFund DAO management believes that the value of EarthFund‚Äôs interest in Newco (i.e., 20%) will far exceed the current value of EF DAO on a stand-alone basis.
* EarthFund DAO and Newco will work closely together to maintain a fair ecosystem for DAO communities on Newco‚Äôs platform.
* EarthFund DAO will receive quarterly shareholder updates from Newco
* **EarthFund DAO will be responsible for the ‚ÄòBrowse Communities‚Äô** section of the Newco platform (what communities are included, featured, removed, etc.)
* **EarthFund DAO will be entitled to their pro-rata share of sales proceeds if Newco is sold.**
* **EarthFund DAO will receive its pro-rata distributions from the profits of Newco if Newco chooses to distribute profits (vs. reinvest).**
* EarthFund DAO will have a vote on how it uses distributions or possible sales proceeds.


## **Have your say**

Voting to approve this proposal will allow EarthFund to seek the investment it needs to continue growing and developing the platform despite market conditions. 

It is our goal to use the investment to grow the EarthFund platform into one of Web3.0‚Äôs biggest companies and aim for these stretch goals in the next 12 months: 


* launch 1000+ communities
* Raise $100M in donations
* Facilitate $5M in community rewards
* Fund 20K+ world-saving grants

### Voting approval can help us make these goals a reality. 

Thank you, as always, for your support.

title: Pink Planet 50/25/25 raffle for compensation plan.
description:
Idea: special NFTs that are raffle numbers for Pink Planet.
50% paid to winner.
25% paid to compensation
25% sent to gamma reserves

Post compensation:
50% paid to winner
50% sent to gamma reserves

Key points:
1. Pay back compensation plan faster.
2. Put buying pressure on gamma and increase APYs across Planet. 
3. Increase Gamma reserves for future payouts. 
4. More fees to burn aqua, grow reserve, grow treasury.
4. Fun way of making money while supporting protocol and community.  

Each raffle ticket can cost $5 in stable coin which gets converted to gamma at that moment of buying. The gamma is lock in their raffle ticket until the drawing at the 1st of each month. Winner of the raffle receives 50% and sent to their gamma IV.  25% will to be  sent to the gamma compensation available to claim.  The time it enters the gamma claim vault, the dollar amount of gamma worth at that moment is deducted from the compensation plan. Claiming gamma for compensation gets rewards sent to IV. When the compensation plan is all paid back. Change the raffle to 50% goes  to the winner. 50% goes to gamma reserves. 

Raffles are an easy and fun way to excite a new audience. Everyone likes to win money. As more users come to Planet, they can see the amount up to win and will be excited to purchase a ticket and contribute to protocol growth.

Participate in crafting the new Heroez digital experience!
description:
> Heroez ambitions to create a 360¬∞ fan-centric esport experience. Part of this experience will be a digital experience, through a dedicated web application. The idea is to build this experience in an iterative way, basing our product choices on community feedback, with the objective to delight the Heroez community. To achieve it, in order to orient the first design & development efforts, we ask you to tell us what are the most important needs/desires you want us to address first.

The option that will get the most votes will be the first addressed in our product roadmap. This time, it's a **quadratic voting**, meaning that each voter may spread voting power across any number of choices. The results will reflect both the voting power distributed and the number of contributors who voted for a certain option.

### Option 1

**"I want to follow the activity of the Heroez esport team(s)"**

The idea is to give you more visibility and news on the esport teams' present and future.

Possible features: team roadmap, competitive calendar, tournaments agenda & ranking, Twitch live cast with commentator, team news (articles, photos, videos), players profiles & perf / analytics, game debrief...

### Option 2

**"I want to engage with the Heroez community"**

The idea is to enable our community members better interact with other members, players and management, both in the digital and physical world. 

Possible features: create an event, book an event, follow socials, lives, conferences & AMAs, subs, display Heroez land in the metaverse...
In app messaging and forum would however remain in Discord.

### Option 3

**"I want to participate in Heroez strategic decisions"**

As Heroez is a DAO, NFT holders have a right to participate in strategic decisions. As of today, we are using Snapshot to enable our holders to vote for strategic decisions. In the future web app, we could add software integrations enabling you to access directly to the proposals. 

Possible features: review proposal, make proposal, vote, check the vote's results, elect a council, run for council elections...It is not our ambition to become a software for DAO management, so the main idea here is to build strong integrations (API) with tools like Snapshot, Wonder,...

### Option 4

**"I want to work for Heroez"**

To build a strong DAO, the idea is to empower our community to participate in Heroez operations by performing tasks to help the project grow. 

Possible features: review tasks, apply for tasks, receive payment...It is not our ambition to become a software for DAO management, so the main idea here is to build strong integrations (API) with tools like Wonder which already have dedicated features for that.

### Option 5

**"I want to support Heroez esport club / I want to show I belong to Heroez"**

The idea is to enable our community members show their belonging to Heroez / support financially the activity of the club.

Possible features: Display Heroez NFTs, buy NFTs...Here we would also consider building strong integrations with specialized applications or marketplaces (eg: OpenSea).

title: Shibadoge 'Diamond Hand Globe'
description:
Imagine the fun and utility of a map of the world which shows where our diamond hands are all over the globe! 
A 3D website is created for holders of Shibadoge and Burn token (and or NFT's) to enter in which country they reside in the world. Holders remain completely anonymous, not signing any wallet or a social media handle.... just selecting the token they own and their country from a dropdown menu.
Once they select the country it pins a 'diamond hand' to the location, and 'shades' the area of the map in a different color. The website records the holder as a 'count' of holders in the country and does not record anything else.
 For example, once the first holder in a country is recorded the 'diamond hand' is pinned to that location, then from there on each record becomes a tally of holders that is accumulated, 2,3,4,5 and so on.
This data may be very useful in showing areas where our holders are dominant and maybe where we need to focus on gaining more holders. But also creates a fun aspect to it spinning the 3D globe on your smartphone seeing where are diamond holders are.
This of course is reliant on holders going onto the website and entering their country, however if they are true 'diamond hands' in the project they will want to be engaged and contribute :)
This also can be taken a step further, we could pin investment/crypto events in specific locations on the map to highlight to holders to go an attend these events and market and shill the project. For example , blockchain or crypto conventions, influencer meetups.
Cost: $funds to develop the website
#Shibadoge2theMoon

title: 1 Dogecoin + 1 Shiba Inu = 1 Shibadoge
description:
We have had some great ‚Äòfaucet‚Äô ideas on this dao where we distribute 1 token every second every day to every person in the world. My idea is a similar concept but focuses on our niche markets Dogecoin and Shiba Inu token communities and bringing them together as one to Shibadoge.
Holders that hold 1 Dogecoin plus 1 Shiba Inu token get 1 Shibadoge token!
For example, if a holder has 100,000 dogecoins and 10 million Shiba inu tokens
they will receive 100,000 Shibadoge tokens. So they will need to match both
tokens up to receive the equal amount of Shibadoge. Very much like the matching of our nfts in order to breed a 'Shibadoge' nft.
We will need a platform similar to the staking warzone where holders of Doge+Shiba can claim their Shibadoge, by signing in showing the holdings of both tokens in their wallet(s).
Because our market cap is a lot smaller at the moment the amount of tokens distributed will not be too significant but this is purely a marketing incentive to gain more holders and bring Dogecoin and Shiba Inu communities together.
If it gets both communities engaged and creates exposure for Shibadoge, it will have served it's purpose.
We could open up this platform on random 1 day blocks and cap the amount
of tokens given away on that day to open for 24hrs only.
We could even get a little creative on different days and make it 1 + 1 = 2,3, 4 or 5! Similar to the 'Mint Monday' deals.
The constraints are that people may exploit it by transferring the Dogecoin and Shiba Inu to multiple wallets to claim, however the number of tokens will not be of significant value enough for an incentive to go to the trouble of exploiting this.
Who knows it might even be a good idea to encourage claiming from multiple wallets‚Ä¶just as long as its limited time and a token cap that can be claimed. Our holder count goes up which would look favourable to the market for new holders.
Open to different methods and strategies lets discuss as a community.
Cost: $funds to develop the platform
#Shibadoge2theMoon
